            <p style="line-height: 25px; font-size: 18px;">
                At the heart of our culinary philosophy lies a deep commitment to farm-to-table dining, where every dish begins with fresh, locally-sourced ingredients. Our menu is a celebration of the seasons, featuring an ever-changing array of flavors that highlight the best of what the local farms offer. From crisp, garden-picked vegetables to free-range meats and artisanal cheeses, each ingredient is carefully selected to ensure the highest quality and taste. Our chefs artfully blend tradition with innovation, crafting dishes that not only delight the palate but also tell the story of the land and the hands that nurtured it. Dining with us is more than a meal; it's an intimate journey through the local countryside's bountiful produce and a tribute to the community of farmers and artisans who bring their passion to your plate.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction:row;">
        <div style="width: 50%; height: 700px; padding: 5rem;">
